## 5) StringInserts Index Reference (Verified via Microsoft Learn)

**Source:** https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/security/threat-protection/auditing/
**Verified:** 2026-02-26 — cross-referenced with working DFI Edge code and dfi_extract_sensor_v7.py XML parsing.

pywin32 `ReadEventLog` returns `StringInserts` as a tuple. Indices are 0-based and match the `<Data Name="...">` order in the EventData XML.

